text: Party of Slavic Unity of Ukraine is a more radical political party that was created as an off-shot of the Civil Congress of Ukraine before the 1994 Ukrainian parliamentary election. The Party of Slavic Unity of Ukraine is a Ukrainian branch of the Russian National Unity.Left-center parties.
